## Limitations
The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The search was limited to online resources, which may exclude some print-only publications. Additionally, the cultural dynamics in counseling are complex and continuously evolving, which may not be fully captured in the current literature. Further research could provide more comprehensive insights into the cultural adaptability of counseling theories.